@startuml
title MiniNet - Architecture Composants & Connecteurs
component APIFrontend as "APIFrontend\n(Express / REST)"
component UserManager
component PostManager
component MessageService
component NotificationService
component Storage as "SQLite Storage"
APIFrontend --> UserManager : REST (register/auth/friends)
APIFrontend --> PostManager : REST (create/getFeed)
APIFrontend --> MessageService : REST (send/getInbox)
UserManager ..> Storage : CRUD utilisateurs/amis
PostManager ..> Storage : CRUD posts
MessageService ..> Storage : CRUD messages
cloud "EventBus (in-memory)" as EventBus
NotificationService --> EventBus : publish notifications
UserManager --> EventBus : subscribe
PostManager --> EventBus : subscribe
MessageService --> EventBus : subscribe
note right of NotificationService
Publie:
- notification.post
- notification.message
end note
@enduml
